The paper presents a python library for the security evaluation of machine learning algorithms against adversarial attacks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SE (Software Engineering). However, given the focus on machine learning algorithms and their vulnerability to attacks, cs.LG and cs.CR are the most likely categories. The paper also mentions the implementation of classification algorithms, which further supports the inclusion of cs.LG as the most likely category.
